snippet.title: Omega Strike -  Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Omega Strike is a Metroidvania game with a huge, open-ended world and multiple playable characters. As Doctor Omega and his mutant armies march toward world domination, only a few brave freedom fighters stand in his way.

Overcome deadly enemies and learn new abilities for your heroes. Explore the
world, find its hidden treasures and upgrade your weapons to defeat Doctor Omega and his evil henchmen. 
Follow Digerati on Twitter @DigeratiDm
